      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHICKEN KNIGHT (2) missed the frame latest when seventh at Gawler (23.19) but scored five back at this track (19.97). Solid record here at the distance winning four races. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. BINNAWAY PEARL (6) comes off an average effort last start when fifth at Gawler over 400m behind Next Thing Uno (23.15) in a Grade 3/4/5. Placed at her previous run. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Likely to be about the money. RED SAID SO (1) crossed over from out wide last start before finishing third (17.20) at Murray Bridge Straight in a Grade 4/5 over 300m. Comes through a solid form race last start. Expected to feature again. EVOLVE (8) has strong claims after a top-three finish at this track and distance last time out.",
